{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"headers"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"headers","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Regional compliance"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Network monitoring","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Firewall restrictions","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Work around corporate firewall rules","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"while preserving all headers and request body content."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}]},{"code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"type":"topic","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}